[external][tehcneko][7764726+tehcneko@users.noreply.github.com]     * {@code SomeClass.equals()} and that class doesn't override the {@code equals()} on some ROMs,
[external][tehcneko][7764726+tehcneko@users.noreply.github.com]     * making you hook {@code Object.equals()} instead.
