[external][tehcneko][7764726+tehcneko@users.noreply.github.com]     * full class name as a string, e.g. {@code java.lang.String} or {@code com.example.MyClass}.
[external][tehcneko][7764726+tehcneko@users.noreply.github.com]     * It will be passed to {@link #findClass} with the same class loader that is used for the target
[external][tehcneko][7764726+tehcneko@users.noreply.github.com]     * method, see its documentation for the allowed notations.
